title: Dakine Chameleon Kite Harness
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Chameleon Kite Harness in our Timber print.
Harness Features:
- Single Power Clip Lock buckle
- 10" [ 25cm ] Stainless steel spreader bar
- Spreader bar pad
- Pre-Curved P.E.B. inner support structure
- Featherweight ES foam molded lumbar pad
- Removable handle and leash attachment
- Single overlap power belt
- Dual sport design
